title: Spacious one bedroom + office lower level duplex in Minneapolis
posting_body: ['Kari Anderson and REI Real Estate & Property Management are proud to present this one bedroom + office, one-bathroom lower level duplex.', 'Built in 1916, the property has both charming and unique features as well as some wonderful updates.', 'On the main floor, there is a nice-sized bedroom along with a smaller room that could be used as a second bedroom, office or play room!', 'The living room and dining room are large and they have interesting woodwork and windows.', 'The bathroom is painted in a soft blue color and gives off the feel of water.', 'Toward the back of the unit, there is a beautifully updated kitchen.', 'There is a small pantry area off of the kitchen and that is also where you will find access to the basement.', 'The basement is clean but unfinished.', 'There is laundry for your convenience and a lot of extra space for storage.', 'The hardwood floors and wood trim are featured throughout.', 'You will also find updated tiles, colors, counters and appliances.', 'There is a huge yard that can be accessed by both lower and upper-level tenants.', 'There is also a small shed in the back as well as designated off-street parking spots.', 'The tenant is responsible for all of the utilities.', 'Lawn care and snow removal are covered in your rent.', 'The home is located in the Cleveland neighborhood in Minneapolis.', 'There are a lot of parks, trails and lakes nearby.', 'You will also find schools, transportation options, shopping and an endless amount of restaurants in the area.', 'Pets will be considered with an additional pet deposit and there are weight and breed restrictions for dogs.', 'Please text or call Kari Anderson at', 'show contact info', 'if you have any questions or if you would like to set up a showing.', 'For assistance with your rental property and also to learn more about property management in the Twin Cities, see <URL>.']
